def validate_ic_number(ic_number):
    pattern = re.compile(r'^\d{6}-\d{2}-\d{4}$')
    if pattern.match(ic_number):
        year = int(ic_number[:2])
        month = int(ic_number[2:4])
        day = int(ic_number[4:6])
        
        if year > 0 and month > 0 and month <= 12 and day > 0 and day <= 31:
            return True
    return False
